title: Lee Women's Ultra Lux Comfort with Flex Motion High Rise Skinny Jean
description: SLIM FIT. With these jeans, you never have to compromise on comfort for a flattering fit. They fit slim and hug your natural curves to accentuate your shape so you can go anywhere with confidence.
FLEX MOTION WAISTBAND. Featuring a flexible, non-binding waistband that never pinches or digs into your middle, these high-waisted jeans are comfortable enough for a long day of sitting.
STRETCH DENIM. Strut with confidence in these high-rise skinny jeans. Made from authentic stretch denim, they move with you for all-day comfort.

A LIFETIME OF QUALITY. For over 100 years, Lee has produced quality apparel with durability and long-lasting construction in mind. Lee is committed to designing clothing that conforms to your body, allowing you to move through life freely.

LEGENDARY DETAILS. These women's jeans are finished with our iconic logo hardware, patch and spade pockets that make Lee jeans unique. Inseam: 27" short, 29" medium, 31" long. Rise: 10.5". Bottom Leg Opening: 10".
Lee Womens Ultra Lux Comfort with Flex Motion High Rise Skinny Jean
